data.description: This beautiful 3-bedroom 3 bath ranch style home is aesthetically pleasing in so many ways.  Foyer opens to a spacious open floor plan where family gatherings and memories are sure to be made.  Living room has picture windows that let in plenty of sunlight & look out over the covered front porch.  The attractive kitchen has a garden window, gas stove, lovely cabinets and a pass through to a separate dining area, where an attractive barn door and rustic flair are sure to impress.  Master bedroom has large ensuite, claw tub, walk-in closet and French doors that open onto the expansive back deck.  Guest bedroom is right off the main bath.  Third bedroom could be used as an office or game room and has private 3/4 bath and door leading to the fenced back yard.  One car attached garage has a wood stove and room for special projects.  Gorgeous, fenced back yard has room for a shop, garden and endless outdoor activities.  Comfortable living all on one level makes this lovely home a must see!
